metadata.description: RESURRXION BEGINS HERE! In the wake of the awesome events of IVX — what will become of the Inhumans? In this oversized special issue— the trial of Maximus! The coming of Marvel Boy! And what is the dark secret of Black Bolt? A special bridging issue between the past of the Inhumans and their future — on Earth and in the stars!
metadata.name: Inhumans Prime
